overview: The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetic
  appeal of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too
  generic. The agent embarked on a comprehensive visual redesign, starting with
  a new, calming sleep-themed color palette and custom CSS utilities. This was
  followed by a complete overhaul of the main form layout, introducing
  decorative background elements, a redesigned progress indicator, and enhanced
  navigation. The welcome screen was transformed with a hero section and
  interactive feature cards. All core UI components, such as checkboxes, radio
  buttons, sliders, and progress bars, received a polished update. Crucially,
  all 14 individual form sections were refactored to adopt a consistent, modern
  card-style grouping and theme-aligned text colors. During this process, a
  console error related to  values being passed to input components was
  identified and resolved by implementing a safe value conversion within the
   component. The outcome is a visually cohesive, professional, and
  calming application experience.
